OL,3,C'The people that need breathing
OL,4,Cequipment should be top of the list'
OL,6,FThere wasn't anybody who escaped the
OL,7,Fstorm completely unscathed in Northern
OL,8,FIreland.
OL,10,FThere was a tragic loss of life in a
OL,11,FDonegal road accident.
OL,13,FSchools lost roofs, trees blocked
OL,14,Fthousands of roads, homes were
OL,15,Fdamaged, a day of work and education
OL,16,Fwas lost for many, and thousands
OL,17,Fstruggled without power in cold homes
OL,18,Ffor days.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
