OL,3,C'The people that need breathing
OL,4,Cequipment should be top of the list'
OL,6,F"On their list they have 26,000 people
OL,7,Fon the critical care list. Even if
OL,8,Fthey did have 26,000 generators, they
OL,9,Fcouldn't possibly man those.
OL,11,F"It takes two people to manage a
OL,12,Fgenerator. So that would be 50 odd
OL,13,Fthousand people that would be needed
OL,14,Fto run these. So that's not a long-
OL,15,Fterm solution.
OL,17,F"So I would like to see that list that
OL,18,Fthey have of 26,000 verified in some
OL,19,Fway that they know what equipment is
OL,20,Fbeing used."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
