OL,3,C'The people that need breathing
OL,4,Cequipment should be top of the list'
OL,6,FShe added: "But what we need is a
OL,7,Fproper response to these.
OL,9,F"When I phone, I shouldn't be one of
OL,10,F26,000 on a critical care list. The
OL,11,Fpeople that need breathing equipment
OL,12,Fshould be the top of the list."
OL,14,FMichaela Hollywood bought a generator
OL,15,Fherself a few years ago after somebody
OL,16,Frelying on electricity in a similar
OL,17,Fway to her passed away in Spain during
OL,18,Fa power outage.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
