OL,3,C'The people that need breathing
OL,4,Cequipment should be top of the list'
OL,6,FShe said she feared that this could
OL,7,Fkill her too. So her family paid
OL,8,Fthousands towards a backup power
OL,9,Fsupply, with the rest funded by a now
OL,10,Fdiscontinued Department for
OL,11,FCommunities grant.
OL,13,F"Losing power really does put me in a
OL,14,Flife-threatening situation. I am
OL,15,Fventilator dependent when I sleep and
OL,16,FI also need to use it during the day,"
OL,17,Fsaid Michaela.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
