OL,3,C'The people that need breathing
OL,4,Cequipment should be top of the list'
OL,6,F"Those sorts of thing can run out of
OL,7,Fpower very, very quickly, I am also
OL,8,Ftube-fed so that needs to have power,
OL,9,Fmy air mattress needs power."
OL,11,F"Every facet of my life depends on
OL,12,Felectricity," she said.
OL,14,FHer medicine also goes off without
OL,15,Frefrigeration, and the hoist to help
OL,16,Fher in an out of bed is also electric
OL,17,Fpowered, so is her wheelchair, so as
OL,18,FMichaela puts it, "it becomes a matter
OL,19,Fof life and death very very quickly".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
