OL,6,FShe wants to see more help for people
OL,7,Fto purchase a generator.
OL,9,F"It's not easy to find that money when
OL,10,Fyou're already a family whose
OL,11,Felectricity bill is four times higher
OL,12,Fthan the average," she said.
